<P>
ANOTHER VIEW OF POMONA URGED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I protest the demeaning of Pomona as a crime-ridden and poverty-stricken city 
(Times, Oct. 29). 
</P>
<P>
You only glorify the crime. Your staff writers need to give both views of 
Pomona and not constantly state that minorities are always the cause of crime 
and violence. 
</P>
<P>
The middle class still lives in Pomona maintaining nice homes and careers. 
