IGNORANT AND INEFFICIENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Peter S. Greenberg's article ("It's Time for Business to Get Back to the 
Basics," Oct. 15) about the lack of service for the traveler is right on 
target. However, it reminds me that during 15 years of almost weekly travel in 
the United States, and a total of nearly 30 months' travel throughout Europe 
