<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 35; Column 3; National Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
40 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
JOBLESS RATE STABLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
WASHINGTON 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The nation's unemployment rate remained steady in October at 5.3% as the 
economy produced an unexpectedly high number of new jobs, but the manufacturing 
sector continued to show signs of weakness, the Labor Department reported 
Friday. 
</P>
