<P>
NEW COMICS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Eight new comics join The Times' Sunday lineup today. They are "Beetle Bailey," 
"Blondie," "Hagar the Horrible," "Hi and Lois," "Broom-Hilda," "Marmaduke," 
"Shoe" and "For Better or Worse." Next Sunday the new lineup will join The 
Times' regular color comics section. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
