<HEADLINE>
<P>
CRITICS' CHOICE: WONDERFUL LIFE: THE BURGESS SHALE AND THE NATURE OF HISTORY BY 
STEPHEN JAY GOULD (W.W. NORTON: $15.95; 347PP.) 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Allan J. Tobin 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
