<P>
L.A. Baptist 37, Marshall Fundamental 0 -- L. A. Baptist quarterback Chris 
Robinson gained 120 yards in 11 carries, scored a touchdown and threw for 
another to lead the Knights to an Alpha League victory at Monroe High. 
</P>
<P>
Four running backs each gained more than 50 yards as L. A. Baptist (7-2, 3-1) 
rolled up 364 rushing yards. Tailback Colyn Van Buren paced the attack with 117 
yards in 12 carries and one touchdown. DANIEL NEHORAI 
