<HEADLINE>
<P>
HIGH SCHOOL FOOTBALL ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ANDY MEYERS 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Montclair Prep 55, Maranatha 0 -- Montclair Prep (9-0, 4-0) scored 42 points in 
the first half in eight plays and ran only 16 in the game at San Marino High. 
</P>
<P>
Montclair Prep's Derek Sparks and Michael Jones rushed six times each. Sparks 
finished with four touchdowns and 132 yards. Jones had 108 yards and three 
scores. ANDY MEYERS 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA110589-0214 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 130633 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 5, 1989, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
