<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA110589-0218 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 130643 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 5, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Opinion; Part M; Page 2; Column 1; Opinion Desk 
