<P>
VOTER TURNOUT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
If we want our citizens to vote each year, why don't we let them include the 
stub they receive after voting with their income tax return and receive a $5 
rebate or credit? 
</P>
<P>
While this might seem like a bribe to many who do not vote, why not? We have to 
do something to get the vote out! 
</P>
<P>
JOAN SIEGEL 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
